title: SpecsSphere
subtitle: Luxury sunglasses providing website
1: A luxury sunglasses providing website with dashboard and ordering system.
2: Different Dashboard interface for admin and non admin user.
3: With Express JS backend with mongodb database.
4: Admin has order access and status change ability
5: Admin can make others admin and add product and delete product.

title: Sylheti Guide
subtitle: An easy Sylheti tour guide booking site
1: A Sylhet tour booking website with tour booking system.
2: Easy user tour management with easy enrollment and cancelation.
3: With Express JS backend with mongodb database.
4: Admin can see others enrollment to set a better tour experience and help you to schedule.
5: Admin can also add new packages from add package.

title: DiabeticNet
subtitle: A network and specialize services for diabetic patients
1: Provides different services related to diabetes specific education.
3: Blogs related to diabetes help to educate and make a community.
4: It provides services related to diabetes related product delivery.
